INSTALL file for App::Yak

The recommended way of installing the distribution and tools is using

cpan, cpanm or similar.

cpanm:

$ cpanm App::Yak

CPAN Shell:

$ cpan App::Yak

I you have downloaded the tar-ball you can unpack it and perform the following steps:

$ perl Makefile.PL
$ make
$ make test
$ make install

For more information on module installation, please visit the detailed CPAN module installation guide: at https://www.cpan.org/modules/INSTALL.html.
